flowchart TD
    A[Run run.bat] --> B[Check Python venv + npm + requirements]
    B --> C[Health check backend 8000]
    C -->|Not running| D[Start uvicorn main:app]
    C -->|Running| E[Skip backend start]
    D --> F[Wait until backend ready]
    E --> G[Health check frontend 5173]
    F --> G
    G -->|Not running| H[Start npm run dev]
    G -->|Running| I[Skip frontend start]
    H --> J[Wait until frontend ready]
    I --> K[Open browser tabs /docs and frontend]
    J --> K

    K --> L[User registers or logs in]
    L --> M[JWT token stored in localStorage]
    M --> N[Enter 30 features or upload CSV/PDF/Image]
    N --> O[Predict only -> /predict]
    N --> P[Submit report -> /submit-report]
    O --> Q[Prediction + probability + medicine guidance]
    P --> R[Persist DB row + generate CSV file]
    R --> S[Download CSV from /reports/report_id/csv]
